TAKEITTOTHEBANK ran in the middle of the pack then came on to the stretch in the seven path. THOUGHTS OF GOLD ran on the outside in the middle of the pack took the turn in the four path, then took to the outside to find a path to advance. ROUGE SUNSET ran in the middle of the pack but faded back mid turn had a slight kick down the stretch but not enough to pass a foe. W. WHITEHOUSE ran with an even pace at the back with no advance.
